fter at hunden gj\u00f8r noe riktig.", "Men for \u00e5 komme tilbake til sp\u00f8rsm\u00e5let hva det egentlig kommer av, det kan ikke atferdsterapeuten gi et endelig svar p\u00e5.", "- Vi vet jo ikke eksakt hva som foreg\u00e5r i hodet p\u00e5 hundene, sier Buvik."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "nyheter"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "nyheter|trondheim"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "db003b3191edda91b2857904c06b9eeaf28e88ba5a5fcfed1ae820dd65cdaa90"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2014-05-13T18:25:37.807Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Hvorfor uler Harald n\u00e5r han h\u00f8rer sirener fra redningsbilene?"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9665609.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-default/harald-16-9.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/860d44e16da70dead6b83e9184f2cbdb1f4de872.jpg?598e019c"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Se hunden som uler til n\u00f8detatene -adressa.no", "Forskjellige lyder", "Bel\u00f8nning"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "860d44e16da70dead6b83e9184f2cbdb1f4de872"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["utenriks", "innenriks", "trondheim", "E6", "midtbyen", "bybrann", "bilulykker"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "utenriks,innenriks,trondheim,E6,midtbyen,bybrann,bilulykker"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["nyheter", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "pets"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["hund", "atferdsterapeuten forklarer"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": "harald"}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": "trondheim"}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": "turid buvik"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["nyheter", "nyheter/trondheim"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article9665609.ece/ALTERNATES/w980-d